; Regression test for issue #589: Add ability to control color output (BZ#589)
; https://github.com/ledger/ledger/issues/589
;
; Tests that --no-color and --force-color flags are available and work correctly.
; --no-color suppresses ANSI color codes in output
; --force-color emits ANSI codes even when stdout is not a TTY

2024/01/01 Test
    Expenses:Food    $10.00
    Assets:Cash

2024/02/01 Test2
    Expenses:Food    $-5.00
    Assets:Cash

test bal --no-color
              $-5.00  Assets:Cash
               $5.00  Expenses:Food
--------------------
                   0
end test
